16/01/2005
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- European Commissioner for Enlargement Olli Rehn called on Bulgaria and Romania to step up efforts to meet the EU accession criteria, in a statement for the Bulgarian-language BBC programme Friday (14 January). Rehn said the two countries have a lot to do, particularly in reforming their judicial sectors. (Sega - 15/01/05; Mediapool - 14/01/05)
